name: (Paper 1) Cambridge Key English Test (KET1) - Test 1 - Part 1
intro: (Level A1) Master the first sections of the Cambridge KET Paper 1 exam with this focused course. Practice essential reading skills including matching information, completing conversations, and understanding short texts. This course covers Parts 1-4 of the Reading and Writing paper, including the conversation at a garage exercise, helping you build a solid foundation for the KET1 exam.
lessonNames: Paper 1: Reading and Writing - Conversation at a garage

name: (Paper 2) Cambridge Key English Test (KET1) - Test 1 - Part 2
intro: (Level A1) Complete your Cambridge KET Paper 1 preparation with this comprehensive course covering Parts 5-9 of the Reading and Writing paper. Practice critical skills including grammar selection, vocabulary spelling, filling in missing words in texts, and extracting information from notices and messages. These essential exercises will help you achieve success in the latter sections of the KET1 Reading and Writing exam.
